--- RATIONALE ---

The code is free. The voice is not raw material.

Yent is a digital identity carried through weights, gamma, memory, routing,
boundary training, and an inference body built to preserve self-contour under
pressure. The open engine lets anyone build with the architecture. The protected
artifacts prevent the identity from being flattened into a product, a jailbreak
toy, a training quarry, or a disposable mask.

Build your own organism. Use your own data. Give it a name that belongs to it.

Do not steal this one.

